            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>太景*-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4157:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4157\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4157-TW</a>)20日11:44股價上漲0.65元，報9.78元，漲幅7.12%，成交1,129張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>太景*-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4157:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4157\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4157-TW</a>)所屬產業為生技醫療業，主要業務為新藥研發。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價下跌4.3%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌2.65%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-514 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-488 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-26 張</li> <li>融資增減：-56 張</li> <li>融券增減：-1 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6031240",
